 " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 27 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 
"" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"\")%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F()F*F'F(F(*
